Dear {!Booking__r.Primary_Applicant_Name__c},

Greetings from Runwal Enterprises!

This is a reminder regarding the outstanding payment for your purchased unit. Please find the details below:

Project: {!Booking__r.Project__r.Name}
Unit Number: {!Booking__r.Unit_No__r.Name}
Demand Number: {!RW_Billing_Document_Number__c}
Milestone: {!RW_Demand_Milestone__c}
Outstanding Amount: ₹{!Remaining_Amount__c}
Due Date: {!Due_Date__c}

We request you to kindly clear the dues on or before the due date to avoid any additional late payment charges.

You may also view the demand details on the Runwal Connect App.

If you have already completed the payment, please disregard this message.

Warm regards,
Runwal Enterprises
